Kelly, seriously?

126
00:08:38,160 --> 00:08:40,700
两包维珍妮牌女士香烟和一瓶帕科香水
Two packs of Virginia Slims and a bottle of Paco Rabanne.

127
00:08:40,700 --> 00:08:42,620
每个人都是有价的
Everyone has their price.

128
00:08:42,620 --> 00:08:45,540
幸好刚才我的羊水没破 天啊
I'm just lucky that my water didn't break in there. Oh, God.

129
