Now, the baby bump, dry-clean only.

132
00:08:53,090 --> 00:08:56,590
好的 我记下了 还有 欧米茄确认了下周的安排
Yes, I have that noted. A-Also, Omega confirmed for next week,

133
00:08:56,590 --> 00:08:57,800
