how you feel about roses. You know how I feel about roses.

137
00:09:03,890 --> 00:09:08,270
还有 约翰又来电了 他想在星期二带你去吃晚餐
Also, John called. Again. He wants to take you to dinner Tuesday.

138
00:09:08,270 --> 00:09:10,980
告诉他我搬到洛杉矶去了 给陶氏化学的布鲁斯打电话
Tell him I moved to LA. And call Bruce from Dow Chemical.

139
