好 坐下吧
Okay. Sit down.

1559
01:36:17,670 --> 01:36:18,790
好 都听着
All right, listen up!

1560
01:36:24,970 --> 01:36:26,430
无论今天这里发生什么
Whatever happens here today,

1561
01:36:26,430 --> 01:36:29,430
我都会支持你们做出的每一个决定
I will stand by every decision that you make.

1562
01:36:30,640 --> 01:36:34,020
近十年来 超过四十万人参与了这项计划
Over 400,000 people have worked on this program for nearly ten years.

1563
01:36:34,020 --> 01:36:36,270
就为了实现一个人对全世界的承诺
All to keep one man's promise to the world.

1564
01:36:37,730 --> 01:36:38,860
让我们坚守这个承诺吧
So, let's keep it.

1565
