CFAT CSE 现在能回答“就绪”了吗?
CFAT. CSE, can you give me a "go" now?

1577
01:37:07,050 --> 01:37:08,130
CSE就绪
CSE is go.

1578
01:37:08,130 --> 01:37:10,350
好 鹰号就绪
Okay. Uh, Eagle is go.

1579
01:37:25,780 --> 01:37:27,780
CBTS 这里是CSA9号
CBTS, this is CSA 9.

1580
01:37:27,780 --> 01:37:29,740
倒计时20秒
Twenty seconds and counting.

1581
01:37:31,200 --> 01:37:34,080
倒计时15秒 制导系统已切换为自主模式
T-minus 15 seconds. Guidance is internal.

1582
01:37:35,700 --> 01:37:39,420
十二 十一 十 九...
Twelve, eleven, ten, nine...

1583
01:37:41,460 --> 01:37:43,170
点火程序启动
Ignition sequence starts.

1584
01:37:55,350 --> 01:38:00,100
五 四 三 二 一
Five, four, three, two, one.

1585
01:38:00,100 --> 01:38:01,600
所有引擎启动
All engines running.

1586
01:38:30,260 --> 01:38:32,260
发射 火箭升空
Liftoff. We have liftoff.

1587
01:38:40,310 --> 01:38:41,390
发射塔已分离
Tower clear.

1588
01:38:43,350 --> 01:38:45,270
休斯敦 交给你了
Houston, she's all yours.

1589
01:39:57,640 --> 01:39:59,890
莫·伯克斯来了 要找你们俩
Moe Berkus is here. For both of you.

1590
01:40:00,600 --> 01:40:02,470
阿波罗11号已经升空
Apollo 11 is on the way.

1591
01:40:02,480 --> 01:40:04,560
四十万公里之外
250,000 miles away,

1592
01:40:04,560 --> 01:40:08,860
月球在等待人类的首次到来
where the moon is waiting for man's first arrival.

1593
01:40:08,860 --> 01:40:11,070
整个航程要用三天时间
Flight to take, uh, three days.

